            "family": {
                "name": "Leech",
                "type": "monster_family",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "name": "Leech Species",
                        "type": "section",
                        "text": "The spotted hooktooth leech is often found in areas frequented by trolls, who sometimes wear them as awful decorations, relying on their regeneration to control the bleeding effects. The gigantic elephant leech feeds on immense beasts of the swamplands or jungles, like elephants and dinosaurs, attacking from unexpected range. But it\u2019s the relatively small gutleech that provides the most fuel for nightmares, due to its awful habit of feeding on victims from inside.",
                        "sources": [
                            {
                                "type": "source",
                                "name": "Monster Core 2",
                                "link": {
                                    "type": "link",
                                    "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 212",
                                    "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 212",
                                    "game-obj": "Sources",
                                    "aonid": 276
                                },
                                "page": 212
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ],
                "alternate_link": {
                    "type": "alternate_link",
                    "game-obj": "MonsterFamilies",
                    "aonid": 141,
                    "alternate_type": "legacy"
                },
                "sources": [
                    {
                        "type": "source",
                        "name": "Monster Core 2",
                        "link": {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "Monster Core 2 pg. 212",
                            "alt": "Monster Core 2 pg. 212",
                            "game-obj": "Sources",
                            "aonid": 276
                        },
                        "page": 212
                    }
                ],
                "aonid": 606,
                "game-obj": "MonsterFamilies",
                "monster_family": {
                    "name": "Leech",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "monster_family"
                },
                "game-id": "4d1a375c0d2ba7218d6a47d407742b47",
                "text": "Though valued by apothecaries and field medics as methods to reduce swelling or drain blood, leeches are despised by most who encounter them, regardless of the setting. Young leeches are prized most because their size makes them easier to control in medicinal settings. As a result, those who are willing to hunt and capture them can command high prices due to the risks involved.",
                "edition": "remastered",
                "link": {
                    "type": "link",
                    "name": "Leech",
                    "alt": "Leech",
                    "game-obj": "MonsterFamilies",
                    "aonid": 606
                }
            },
